r\n	<li>Collateral</li>\r\n	<li>Websites</li>\r\n	<li>Banner ads</li>\r\n	<li>HTML emails</li>\r\n	<li>Catalogs</li>\r\n	<li>Packaging</li>\r\n	<li>Direct mail</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensional mailers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Graphic Production</h5>\r\nThe technical skills and craftsmanship that make\r\nthe design a reality.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Page Layout</li>\r\n	<li>Re-sizing</li>\r\n	<li>Color correction</li>\r\n	<li>Retouching &amp; compositing</li>\r\n	<li>Print production</li>\r\n	<li>HTML/CSS markup</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Complete more work. Faster.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '266-revision-21', '', '', '2011-01-07 23:23:35', '2011-01-07 23:23:35', '', 266, 'http://www.herodesignstudio.com/266-revision-21/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
